Is there a better grouping?
Maybe [4, 3, 1]? 25.60 + 21.60 + 8.00 = 55.20 (worse)
Maybe [4, 2, 2]? 25.60 + 15.20 + 15.20 = 56.00 (worse)
Maybe [3, 3, 2]? 21.60 + 21.60 + 15.20 = 58.40 (worse)
So greedy works.

